Josh Kroenke has jetted back to the US with the managerial appointment virtually done, having stayed in London for an extended period to smooth the transition from Unai Emery. Arteta is set to sign a 3.5yr contract and earn a salary package of &pound;5m pa [<br />
@SamiMokbel81_DM<br />
]

